{"tid":2166704,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支爆稻草：前黨校教師前黨員蔡霞","createTime":"2020-08-20T14:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T14:56:42.000Z","uid":266362,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"85e8b58763c9dc1e4d46c15cacf5c2d42dec8e6c","tid":2166704,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T14:40:22.000Z","msg":"不信不信還雖信<br />\n支～爆～了～<br />\n<br />\n相當佩服蔡霞女士的勇敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1、話X係黑幫老大<br />\n2、話X將整個中國倒退了100年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3、話X蠢到極點<br />\n4、話X 2013年唔俾黨員中高層幹部放工攪聚會、同學會、同鄉會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: 2020年8月20日年代向錢看<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFGBH7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFGBH7g.png&h=95e71d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GqoHDFW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGqoHDFW.png&h=384268ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cAQyLmh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcAQyLmh.png&h=b0911edc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HqbFqmE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqbFqmE.png&h=12ef95e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2B2DG3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2B2DG3.png&h=b7584b5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2eda03967071b74ac1e1cc9a482ca0d743c112c9","tid":2166704,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:12:58.000Z","msg":"希望有更多黨員發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4f53114162db1bceef1c0ecef62e64c666864a","tid":2166704,"uid":39488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2eda03967071b74ac1e1cc9a482ca0d743c112c9","tid":2166704,"uid